  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10,
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style='font-family:Inter,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding:12px 16px;color:#d8d9da;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px'><div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:0 0 8px 0'>How to Trigger</p><div style='background:#1a1b1f;border:1px solid #2c3235;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 16px;font-family:monospace;font-size:0.85rem;color:#73bf69;word-break:break-all'>$ oha -z 60s -c 10 -m POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{\"events\":[{\"order_id\":\"20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001\",\"log_line\":\"x\"}]}' http://localhost/api/analytics/events</div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:16px 0 4px 0'>Location</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0;font-family:monospace'>service-d/src/handlers.rs — process_events() ~line 154</p></div><div><p style='font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#ff9830;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin:0 0 8px 0'>What's Happening</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0 0 10px 0'>Service D processes analytics events in a loop. On every iteration it calls <code style='background:#1a1b1f;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px'>Regex::new(...)</code> to compile the same pattern for extracting order IDs. Regex compilation is expensive — roughly 1000× slower than matching with a pre-compiled regex.</p><p style='font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;color:#8e8e8e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 4px 0'>How to identify</p><ul style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0 0 10px 0;padding-left:16px'><li>Pyroscope flame graph: <code style='background:#1a1b1f;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px'>Regex::new</code> appears as a wide, hot frame</li><li>Service D p99 latency is elevated even at low request rates</li><li>CPU usage scales linearly with request rate rather than levelling off</li></ul><p style='font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:600;color:#8e8e8e;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 4px 0'>The Fix</p><p style='font-size:0.83rem;color:#aaa;margin:0'>Move <code style='background:#1a1b1f;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px'>Regex::new(...)</code> above the loop so the pattern is compiled once and reused for every event.</p></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "gridPos": { "h": 12, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "type": "flamegraph",
      "title": "Service D - CPU Flame Graph",
      "datasource": { "uid": "pyroscope", "type": "grafana-pyroscope-datasource" },
      "description": "Look for Regex::new calls burning CPU in the flame graph",
      "targets": [
        {
          "profileTypeId": "process_cpu:cpu:nanoseconds:cpu:nanoseconds",
          "labelSelector": "{service_name=\"service-d-analytics\"}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Service D - Request Latency (p95, p99)",
      "description": "High latency from CPU-bound regex compilation",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-d-analytics\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_latency_bucket{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-d-analytics\"}[1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 20 },
          "unit": "ms"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22 },
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Service D - Request Rate",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{span_kind=\"SPAN_KIND_SERVER\",service=\"service-d-analytics\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "Requests/sec",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      }
    },
